OL,3,CDriving bans and bank account snooping
OL,4,Cpowers planned for benefit fraudsters
OL,6,FBenefit cheats could be banned from
OL,7,Fdriving if they repeatedly fail to pay
OL,8,Fback cash to the taxpayer, under a new
OL,9,Fgovernment drive to crackdown on
OL,10,Fwelfare fraud.
OL,12,FThe Department for Work and Pensions
OL,13,F(DWP) will also be able to recover
OL,14,Fmoney directly from fraudsters' bank
OL,15,Faccounts.
OL,17,FThe Public Authorities (Fraud, Error
OL,18,Fand Recovery) Bill, which would put
OL,19,Fthe measures into law, is due to be
OL,20,Fintroduced in Parliament today.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
