OL,3,CDriving bans and bank account snooping
OL,4,Cpowers planned for benefit fraudsters
OL,6,FIt will help save the taxpayer #1.5
OL,7,Fbillion over the next five years, the
OL,8,FDWP estimates.
OL,10,FOnce the Bill is made law, benefit
OL,11,Fcheats could be disqualified from
OL,12,Fdriving for up to two years if they
OL,13,Frefuse to repay money they owe.
OL,15,FCourts could suspend fraudsters'
OL,16,Fdriving licences following application
OL,17,Fby the DWP, if they owe welfare debts
OL,18,Fof more than #1,000 and have ignored
OL,19,Frepeated requests to pay it back.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
