OL,3,CDriving bans and bank account snooping
OL,4,Cpowers planned for benefit fraudsters
OL,6,FThe department will also have powers
OL,7,Fto get bank statements from people
OL,8,Fthey believe have enough cash to pay
OL,9,Fback welfare debts, but are refusing
OL,10,Fto do so.
OL,12,FThe DWP however insists it will not
OL,13,Fhave direct access to people's bank
OL,14,Faccounts.
OL,16,F"We are turning off the tap to
OL,17,Fcriminals who cheat the system and
OL,18,Fsteal law-abiding taxpayers' money,"
OL,19,FWork and Pensions Secretary Liz
OL,20,FKendall said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
