OL,3,CDriving bans and bank account snooping
OL,4,Cpowers planned for benefit fraudsters
OL,6,FShe added: "This means greater
OL,7,Fconsequences for fraudsters who cheat
OL,8,Fand evade the system, including as a
OL,9,Flast resort in the most serious cases
OL,10,Fremoving their driving licence.
OL,12,F"Backed up by new and important
OL,13,Fsafeguards including reporting
OL,14,Fmechanisms and independent oversight
OL,15,Fto ensure the powers are used
OL,16,Fproportionately and safely."
OL,18,FIn an attempt to provide assurance
OL,19,Fabout the Bill, ministers will bring
OL,20,Fforward codes of practice for those
OL,21,Fwho will use the new powers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
