OL,6,FShe added: "But having knowingly
OL,7,Fappointed a convicted fraudster to his
OL,8,Fcabinet, Keir Starmer cannot be
OL,9,Ftrusted to get tough on fraud.
OL,11,F"Labour must do more to tackle the
OL,12,Fspiralling welfare budget, and explain
OL,13,Fwhy they are yet to match our #12
OL,14,Fbillion in savings - raising the
OL,15,Fprospect that Rachel Reeves will be
OL,16,Fback again later this year with
OL,17,Fanother tax raid on working people."
